        {
          "text": "and are the only fighters with large lifestealing abilities (not given by equipment or emblems)."
        },
        {
          "text": "Additionally, they are some of the few heroes that can heal themselves with their skills without specific equipment, along with with, and  with."
        },
        {
          "text": "is the only one who can transform in the early game and change his mode of attack."
        },
        {
          "text": "is only the hero can throw any hero (allied and enemy alike), monster or minion (excluding Turtle and Lord)."
        },
        {
          "text": "His allies cannot longer be thrown when his allies have until purchase back to."
        },
        {
          "text": "is the only hero who can summon clones of himself (only for a limited time like Guinevere's second skill)."
        },
        {
          "text": "can also summon herself but it has limited-time to vanish via without affecting her hitpoints."
        },
        {
          "text": "is the only fighter whose can damage a defensive turret."
        },
        {
          "text": "and are the only heroes that switch to a different weapon when using their ultimate skills ( and  respectively)."
        },
        {
